      <title>美联储降息抵消油价暴跌影响，海湾伊斯兰债券涨势增强</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-16/gulf-sukuk-rally-grows-as-fed-rate-cuts-outweigh-oil-s-plunge</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于投资者摆脱了原油价格暴跌的影响，转而将注意力转向美联储即将实施的宽松政策，石油资源丰富的波斯湾地区的伊斯兰证券上周创下了自 2021 年 2 月以来最长的周涨幅。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-16/gulf-sukuk-rally-grows-as-fed-rate-cuts-outweigh-oil-s-plunge</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 16 Sep 2024 08:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
